para_trans: Eighth Economic Census 2025-26 Corrigendum on the constitution of committees at various levels
Government Correctional Certificate No: ASAN 2025 / Q.No.155 / Ka-1417
Martyr Rajguru Chowk, Madam Cama Road,
Reference: - Planning Department Government Decision No: ASAN / Q. No.155 / Ka-1417 dated 6th January, 2025

Government Refinement Paper: - The 8th National Economic Census will be conducted by the Central Government in 2025-2026 and committees have been constituted at various levels under the Government Resolution dated 6th January, 2025 in this regard for time bound implementation of the Census and for effective regulation and coordination of sectoral activities.
2. In the said Government Decision, Table No. Changes related to serial number Lo in 5.19 are being made as follows.

In cases of districts where an adequate number of Joint Directors / Deputy Directors is not available for appointment of Member Secretaries on the Coordination Committee as per the classification of Municipal Corporations, officers of the rank of at least Deputy Director in the Regional Office or other district of the concerned Division shall act as Member Secretary of the Committee.
The Member Secretaries for the mentioned Municipal Corporations in the districts of Thane, Palghar and Raigad shall be as follows.
table_trans: Joint Director, Directorate of Finance and Information Technology, Regional Law Officer (for Class A and Class B Municipal Corporations.) Deputy Director, Directorate of Finance and Statistics, Regional Office and Divisional Nodal Officer or Deputy Director, District Statistics Office (for Class B, Class C and Class D Municipal Corporations.)

para_trans: The Government Corrigendum is available on the Government of Maharashtra website www.maharashtra.gov.in.

Deputy Director, Divisional Kayalaya, Konkan Division
Deputy Director, Regional Office, Konkan Division
